ntion":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"cry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"Harumi","body":"I think this'll make it easier for me to ask my boss to try even more new things.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"I see. So ticket sales will influence what we as a band can do.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event184-05-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"Harumi","body":"Not entirely, but they're one thing that'll be factored in when making future decisions.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"Harumi","body":"The agency has to look at shows from a business point of view.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"True. They can't just put on our shows for the fun of it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event184-05-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"Harumi","body":"Right. We need to have a good feel for what kind of potential a band might have.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"So, does that mean we've shown them we have lots of potential?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event184-05-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"Harumi","body":"You've shown them you have plenty! Your debut show sold out. That's huge. Not every artist can do that.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"Harumi","body":"But you girls did! This is going to open a lot of doors for you!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"Our show has not even started yet. Perhaps, you're speaking a little prematurely.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event184-05-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"You won't know for sure... until after you have seen tomorrow's show...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event184-05-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"Harumi","body":"My mind is already made up! I know you all are going to rock the house tomorrow. It's a Roselia show!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Fufu. You've got a lotta faith in us. But I'm sure happy to hear it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event184-05-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"Yes. We will not disappoint.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event184-05-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"Harumi","body":"All right. The final blog post before tomorrow's show is up.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"Harumi","body":"... Ah, people are commenting already.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"Harumi","body":"\"I was waiting for this! Lately, I've been checking this blog every day. I'm so excited for the debut show!\"","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"Harumi","body":"\"I'm happy I got to see Roselia practicing... I was worried their music might change, but they sound the same. I'm sure the show will be great now~.\"","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"Harumi","body":"\"I discovered Roselia through this blog, and then I bought their mini album! It's amazing! I'm going to tomorrow's show!\"","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":222,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":222}],"windowDisplayName":"Harumi","body":"...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFacto